# Koe — terminology dictionary (EXAMPLE)
#
# Copy this file to `dictionary.txt` (or just edit dictionary.txt, which is
# created automatically on first run) and add your own terms.
# This file stays 100% local and is never uploaded anywhere.
#
# 1 line = 1 entry. Write proper nouns / jargon so they transcribe correctly:
#     Kubernetes
#     PostgreSQL
#
# Use 'heard => canonical' to auto-correct a recurring mis-transcription
# (left = what the recognizer hears, right = the spelling you want):
#     クバネティス => Kubernetes
#     ポスグレ => PostgreSQL
#
# Corrections you make from the tray ("correct last output") are appended here.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

